com.io7m.jspatial.api

Interface BoundingVolumeLType

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BoundingVolumeL

    public interface BoundingVolumeLType

    The type of bounding volumes with long integer coordinates.

    Bounding volumes have an inclusive lower bound and an exclusive upper bound.

    Since:
    3.0.0

      • overlaps

        default boolean overlaps(BoundingVolumeLType other)

        Determine whether or not this volume overlaps another given volume.

        Overlapping is reflexive: ∀a. a.overlaps(a) == true

        Overlapping is symmetric: ∀a b. a.overlaps(b) == b.overlaps(a)

        Parameters:
        other - The other volume
        Returns:
        true iff this volume overlaps other

      • contains

        default boolean contains(BoundingVolumeLType other)

        Determine whether or not this volume contains another given volume.

        Containment is reflexive: ∀a. a.contains(a)

        Containment is transitive: ∀a b c. a.contains(b) → b.contains(c) → a.contains(c)

        Containment implies overlapping: ∀a b. a.contains(b) → b.overlaps(a)

        Parameters:
        other - The other volume
        Returns:
        true iff this volume contains other
